1. *Kolega* je pokazao svoju novu sliku. (My colleague showed his new picture.)
2. *Kolegama* sam ponudio da se pridruže našoj grupi. (I offered to my colleagues to join our group.)
3. *Koleginom* sinu se sviđa moja ideja. (My colleague's son likes my idea.)
4. *Kolegi* sam rekao da se slaže sa mnom. (I told my colleague to agree with me.)
5. *Kolegama* sam ponudio da pomognu. (I offered to my colleagues to help.)